{"tid":290013,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]去成人用品店 點知比個黑鬼用假鳩質左我一下","createTime":"2017-06-19T12:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T06:16:32.000Z","uid":19919,"like":13,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5456643d042e9b4993e4673ed89b1459e195de13","tid":290013,"uid":19919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日去左元朗某標名良好日本貨既成人用品店到<br />\n諗住買翻個震蛋或者其他睇岩既野同女友玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到去之後搵嚟搵去都唔見有震蛋 <br />\n仲要好似有d人係到望住我咁 搞到我勁尷尬 <br />\n廢事煩就去左counter到諗住問下到底擺左係邊<br />\n點知個counter竟然係個黑鬼<br />\n<br />\n黑鬼: 🦍 我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我: er... 我想問下呢..呢到有無賣震蛋㗎..<br />\n佢: 🤷🏿&zwj;♂️🤷🏿&zwj;♂️🤷🏿&zwj;♂️🤷🏿&zwj;♂️🤷🏿&zwj;♂️<br />\n我: (指手劃腳 揸實個拳頭扮震)this one leh.. for girls ga<br />\n佢: (拎咗碌XL假鳩出黎) ahhh~ this is a good shit man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我: no ar no ar, like a ball 咁ga<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就指住門口附近嘅位置 我一望埋去 <br />\n即刻好似成功販運左700噸蝦片咁大聲講咗句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呀  呢  㗎  多 ! !</span></span><br />\n當我衝緊過去既時候發現個黑鬼都係個counter到擒緊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪話: it's ok. I get la.<br />\n佢: sup mata? Sup? 之後一碌XL size假鳩一野車埋黎<br />\n仲一路追住我唔放 依家呢埋係個廁所唔敢出去 點做好？"},{"pid":"ac88d8fb3ea3d21a4c4060799980f42b64da91e5","tid":290013,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce166bea7b795f1c4262be96297b6929073a329e","tid":290013,"uid":19919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚臭呀個廁所"},{"pid":"187aef75a377907614ab58f4f06c9721cc3bf230","tid":290